    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>ExistingDBS</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;DBS UPDATE SERVICE CHECK&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I confirm that DBS certificate number &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!What_is_your_DBS_Certificate_Number}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; is the unamended certificate.  The Company will verify and take a copy of the certificate.  The certified copy will be made available to the Company’s Head Office in order to assess my suitability to work in a DBS environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I confirm that I have signed up for the DBS Update Service and my subscription is current.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I agree for the Company to undertake online update check(s) of my DBS status as reasonably necessary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>GeneralText</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;GENERAL&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I understand that I may not be able to work in a DBS environment until the DBS certificate/status has been verified and approval to work in a DBS environment received.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I consent to the Company transmitting and keeping a copy(ies) of my: DBS application; certificate; and any update(s), as necessary, and I consent to The Company sharing the DBS certificate with any client with whom I may be placed on assignment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Name:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt; {!Get_Candidate.FirstName} {!Get_Candidate.MiddleName} {!Get_Candidate.LastName}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Date: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(68, 68, 68);&quot;&gt;{!$Flow.CurrentDate}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;DBS Privacy Policy &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;- standard/enhanced checks (paper applications) declaration: I have read the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/dbs-privacy-policies&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Standard/Enhanced Check Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt; for applicants and I understand how the DBS will process my personal data and the options available to me for submitting an application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;INFORMATION FOR CANDIDATES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Certain roles require candidates to have undergone additional checks with the Disclosure &amp;amp; Barring Service (“DBS”) to see whether they have any convictions (spent or unspent) which may make them unsuitable for work with vulnerable adults and children.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I consent to the DBS providing an electronic result directly to the responsible organisation that has submitted my application. I understand that an electronic result contains a message that indicates either the certificate does not contain criminal record information or to await certificate which will indicate that my certificate contains criminal record information. In some cases, the responsible organisation may provide this information directly to my employer prior to me receiving my certificate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I understand if I do not consent to an electronic result being issued to the responsible organisation submitting my application that I must not proceed with this application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;I understand that to withdraw my consent whilst my application is in progress, I must contact the DBS helpline 03000 200 190. My application will then be withdrawn&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Following the above statement, I understand that should I wish &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;NOT&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt; to provide consent I will contact my employer to withdraw my application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;In order to assess your suitability for a placement in a role that requires a DBS check, we will need to see this certificate.  We must see the original to ensure that nothing has been altered.  You should bring the original certificate into the Company branch and they will verify it &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;and take a copy&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;. This copy will be made available to the Company Head Office in order that your suitability to work in a DBS environment can be assessed and will be shared with clients where necessary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;strongly recommend&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt; that you sign up for the DBS Update Service at the time you fill in the application form.  This can be done online at www.gov.uk/dbs.  If you do not sign up to the DBS Update Service when you submit your application, you will have a further opportunity to sign up within 14 days of the date of the DBS certificate.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;However, if you miss this date you may not be able to sign up for updates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;By signing up for the Update Service you will not have to submit another DBS application form unless there are any changes to your status (e.g. you are convicted of a criminal offence).  We will be able to check online for any updates to your DBS status when required without you having to do anything further.  We cannot do this without your consent, and in any event, the DBS will tell you every time an organisation undertakes an update check on you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;We undertake DBS checks regularly (generally annually) in order to ensure we comply with our obligations to our clients.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Unfortunately, we may not be able to place you in a role which requires a DBS check until you have been assessed or your DBS check is up-to-date.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Please see the Company’s &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.impellam.com/privacy&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Privacy Notice&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt; (copy of which is available on request and on our website) for details of why we collect, process and transfer any personal data or sensitive personal data from you and how we treat that personal data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</text>
    </textTemplates>
    <textTemplates>
        <name>NewDBS</name>
        <isViewedAsPlainText>false</isViewedAsPlainText>
        <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;NEW DBS APPLICATION&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I confirm that by completing and submitting the DBS application form number &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;{!What_is_your_DBS_application_form_number}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 170, 227);&quot;&gt;Blue Arrow&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;(the “Company”) I agree for a DBS check to be undertaken.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I agree that on receipt of the DBS certificate I will immediately bring the original (unamended) into &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 170, 227);&quot;&gt;{!Get_Candidate.Owner.UserRole.Name}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; (Branch/Office) and the Company will verify and take a copy of the certificate.  The certified copy will be made available to the Company Head Office in order to assess my suitability to work in a DBS environment.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I confirm that I will sign up for the DBS Update Service now and, whilst working for the Company, annually at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.gov.uk/dbs&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;www.gov.uk/dbs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;I agree for the Company to undertake online update check(s) of my DBS status as reasonably necessary.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
